            All Events
            <br><br><br>
          %h4
            WARNING:  Deleting an event also deletes the guest list.  Users who registered to attend will not know the event was canceled.  Furthermore, since the guest list (with guest emails) was deleted, you will have no way to reach out to attendees to tell them the event was canceled.   Be sure to get the guest email list and send your own "event canceled" emails out, *before* deleting an event.






        %table#events.table
          %thead
            "People Attending" - No. of people registered to attend the event *through the website*
            <br>
            "Capacity" - Maximum no. of people allowed to register through site
            %tr
              -# Note there are invisible spaces after each of following th titles
              %th Event Name           
              %th Description          
              %th Host          
              %th Start Time                    
              %th End Time                      
              %th Venue                
              %th Address                                 
              %th People Attending
              %th Capacity
          %tbody
            - @events.each do |event|
              %tr
                %td= event.event_name 
                %td= event.description
                %td= event.host
                %td= event.start_date_time.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal)
                %td= event.end_date_time.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal)
                %td= event.venue
                %td= event.address
                %td= event.num_persons_attending
                %td= event.max_capacity
                %td= button_to 'Delete event and *guest list*', event_path(event), :method => :delete, :confirm => 'EXTREMELY IMPORTANT- remember to check if there are site users who already signed up for this event.  Reload this page to get latest info, then check the number of persons registered to attend the event.  "Event canceled" emails do not automatically go out to these people.  Do not delete this event before planning how to send your own "event canceled" notice out to everyone.  As soon as you delete this event, you will lose the guest list storing the email addressed of all the people attending and will have no way to contact them.***                                                                                                                      To leave the event in place, click the CANCEL button below.  Click the OK button to go ahead and delete the event and its guest list.'

        %p
        %p
